Text: I'm digging this show! Thanks EZ!!

Also, SyFy ditched sci-fi it sees. TV channels have really lost focus of who shows what.

Loving the show. Have it on PVR, but can't transfer it off for device use!
Maraming Salamat Sa Inyo. Napaka Kasaiya Siya.
